{"tid":2293400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣空軍後勤預算由102億元大增至明年159億元 鞏固後勤維修能力 避免再發生撼事","createTime":"2020-11-20T08:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T13:20:00.000Z","uid":292499,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2bec6b5aa1d3c79687003d622d3a0907dbb8d8f2","tid":2293400,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T08:09:31.000Z","msg":"趙天麟追問，空軍維修預算109年編列102億元，明年則為159億元，是否因應今年的新局勢發展所增加？黃志偉回應：是的；其中一部分是因應新局勢，另外則為飛機零件與裝備作性能上改進或小型構改工程，現在編列預算能讓戰機壽期管理更確實，「不再發生不幸事件」。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/10930/5027193\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F10930%2F5027193&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=805f4572\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/10930/5027193</a>"},{"pid":"863c1722474633c9d587fe1b3038349d9379c023","tid":2293400,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T08:10:01.000Z","msg":"多50幾億都係好事"},{"pid":"8f2a3ebe08c2095195272b2c2a8156911f02ec7f","tid":2293400,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T08:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29de3ed5e23a2e5ec9a90e35e608ba56f043c524","tid":2293400,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T08:12:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6afb721f840f7ab4d12bf3011fd8baebccf4fdc6","tid":2293400,"uid"